      "content": "the \"hide and seek\" thing is a bit weird lol. can you just give me a concrete example? like if i owe 30,000 at a 5% interest rate, can you show me the actual math for the first month so i can see exactly how much is interest and how much is principal? i just want to see the numbers.",
